// Test 5: Comment Preservation
// All comments should be preserved during formatting

/* This is a block comment before the first expression */
/* It should remain here after formatting */
<<  404684003|Clinical finding|

/* ECL-END */

/* Comment between expressions */
<404684003  OR  <19829001

/* ECL-END */

/* Multi-line comment
   spanning several lines
   should be preserved */
< 404684003 : 363698007 = < 39057004

/* ECL-END */

/* Inline comment after expression */ << 234567890

/* ECL-END */

/* Comment at the end */
